# fypd - Local Environment Configuration
# Copy this file to '.env' and adjust settings to fit your local environment.

# ==============================================================================
# 1. SYSTEM BINARIES & DIRECTORIES
# ==============================================================================
# Path to the ImageMagick executable (required by MoviePy TextClip)
# - Windows default: C:\Program Files\ImageMagick-7.1.2-Q16-HDRI\magick.exe
# - Linux/macOS: Usually auto-detected in PATH or set to '/usr/bin/convert'
# IMAGEMAGICK_BINARY=C:\Program Files\ImageMagick-7.1.2-Q16-HDRI\magick.exe

# Port and Host configurations for the local FastAPI server
# PORT=8000
# HOST=127.0.0.1
